quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,55,"Àti pé dájúdájú wọ́n ti ṣe ohun tó ń bí wa nínú."
  26,56,"Dájúdájú gbogbo wa ni kí á sì wà tìfura-tìfura.”"
  26,57,"Nítorí náà, A mú (ìjọ Fir‘aon) jáde kúrò nínú àwọn ọgbà oko àti ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú omi,"
  27,28,"Mú ìwé mi yìí lọ, kí o jù ú sí wọn. Lẹ́yìn náà, kí o takété sí wọn, kí o sì wo ohun tí wọn yóò dá padà (ní èsì).”"
  27,29,"(Bilƙīs) sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjòyè, dájúdájú wọ́n ti ju ìwé alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé kan sí mi."
  27,30,"Dájúdájú ó wá láti ọ̀dọ̀ (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n. Dájúdájú ó (sọ pé) “Ní orúkọ Allāhu, Àjọkẹ́-ayé, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  28,1,"Tọ̄ sīn mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.){1}.",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  28,2,"Ìwọ̀nyí ni àwọn āyah Tírà tó ń yanjú ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá."
  28,3,"À ń ké nínú ìró (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Fir‘aon fún ọ pẹ̀lú òdodo nítorí ìjọ tó gbàgbọ́ lódodo."